/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2130612%2Forg%2F2a476d94096267658928a58193c1a1aa.jpg%2Fecz2t4l3Z4vUJoSIOJzXuGT3bLSpDcIne5UVwHuVFcA%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=1443e42d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5ecfa95b992dc74b5dda67039d2122cf80c7ac5","tid":1884993,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:25:57.000Z","msg":"不誠實使用電腦！！"},{"pid":"fe88f8e2b4a6a2ac13e1b19dfaeea94ce8293064","tid":1884993,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"大家唔好晒時間諗<br />\n因為唔會諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7bb4331079ce628ec597d2a633a823f1c8708d","tid":1884993,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5ecfa95b992dc74b5dda67039d2122cf80c7ac5","tid":1884993,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:25:57.000Z","msg":"不誠實使用電腦！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:27:11.000Z","msg":"休班警員不誠實用警方電腦<br />\n2014年08月18日<br />\n<br />\n一名加入警隊兩年的警員，因不誠實使用警方電腦，今早在荃灣裁判法院，被判60小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n24歲的被告陳文俊，早前在休班時間，懷疑自己的私家車涉及刑事案件，返回駐守警署，登入警察電腦資料庫查看，因所查看資料與職責無關而被控不誠實使用警方電腦罪，裁判官考慮到他坦白認罪，背景良好，判他接受60小時社會服務令。"},{"pid":"897d2688acc28027051717495c311623455255b1","tid":1884993,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:28:37.000Z","msg":"襲警？"},{"pid":"d0b2c951c82d70703b0e511bac27431836420880","tid":1884993,"uid":44795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:28:38.000Z","msg":"非法集結，暴動"},{"pid":"a685ec0a9e8a67961dcbc87fc89a425621d17d20","tid":1884993,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5edf68d13c2a40aac5ad86841bbd05906779848","tid":1884993,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:59:37.000Z","msg":"有邏輯問題，<br />\n「有咩罪行係黑警未犯過」係法律大於黑警先有違法問題<br />\n現實係黑警大於法律，呢個命題成唔成立都係個問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:37:29.000Z","msg":"黑警就是法律<br />\n現實嚟講佢哋唔會犯法<img src=\"/